**Required output format (plan-state contract — MANDATORY):**

End the response with EXACTLY ONE of these labels on its own line and emit
nothing after it:

```
state:plan-go
state:plan-no-go
state:plan-blocked
```

Use `state:plan-blocked` only when planning cannot proceed without human
feedback or an external dependency. The prose before the final label must say
why it is blocked, identify any blocking issue, and state what unblocks it.
